node.text: Hey Guys ! Have you been reading during this time of being quarantined ? I had the honor on being apart of this Book Promotion thanks to @misstalisha . Check it out and get your book too !! #reading #readmorebooks #rollingthroughlifewithmommy #explore #explorepage #kidreaders #quarantine #lanilove
